Dear <%= @household.name %> Household,

A new statement has been created in Gather for your <%= @community.name %> account.

<% if @statement.total_due >= 0 -%>
The amount due is <%= number_to_currency(@statement.total_due) %>.
<% else -%>
You have a <%= number_to_currency(-@statement.total_due) %> credit balance. No payment is required.
<% end -%>

Please visit the link below to see the details:

<%= statement_url(@statement) %>

<% if @statement.total_due > 0 -%>
Thanks for your prompt payment!
<% end -%>
